description:
Aspose.BarCode for .NET is a robust and reliable barcode generation and recognition component, written in managed C#, it allows developers to quickly and easily add barcode generation and recognition functionality to their Microsoft .NET applications (WinForms, ASP.NET and .NET Compact Framework). 

Aspose.BarCode for .NET supports most established barcode standards and barcode specifications. It has the ability to export to multiple image formats including: BMP, EMF, GIF, JPEG, PNG, TIFF and WMF.
releaseNotes:
The following is a list of improvements and improvements and changes in this release of Aspose.BarCode.

Major features
We have greatly reworked PDF417 recognition. Now our tool can recognize PDF417 barcode much better (BARCODENET-33973).

Other Improvements and Changes
Enhancements:
BARCODENET-13470 Recognize MacroPdf417 barcode from image (containing multiple barcodes)
BARCODENET-18101 Incorrect Pdf417 barcode recognition
BARCODENET-28279 MacroPdf417 barcodes not recognized
BARCODENET-28733 Incorrect codetext recognized from scanned pdf417 images
BARCODENET-33148 PDF417 barcode is not recognized on noisy image
BARCODENET-33326 Pdf417 barcode is not recognized in jpg images.
BARCODENET-33562 Incorrect Pdf417 bar code recognition in JPG image
BARCODENET-33944 Incorrect recognition of PatchCode from the TIF file
BARCODENET-33945 Improve recognition speed for QR
summary: Aspose.BarCode for .NET is a robust and reliable barcode generation and recognition component
title: Aspose.BarCode for .NET
